| **Swimlane / Actor**       | **Tasks / Responsibilities**                                                                                                                  |
| -------------------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Administrator**          | - Register new equipment<br>- Assign department<br>- View reports                                                                             |
| **Maintenance Supervisor** | - Check maintenance requirements<br>- Create maintenance tasks<br>- Assign technicians<br>- Approve completed tasks                           |
| **Technician**             | - Receive assigned maintenance task<br>- Perform maintenance<br>- Update maintenance table (actions, cost, date)                              |
| **System**                 | - Generate alerts for upcoming maintenance or warranty expiry<br>- Store maintenance history automatically<br>- Produce BI reports/dashboards |



Flow Description in Swimlanes Style

[Administrator Lane]
   └── Register Equipment
   └── Assign Department

[Supervisor Lane]
   └── Check Maintenance Requirement
   └── Create Task
   └── Assign Technician
   └── Approve Task Completion

[Technician Lane]
   └── Receive Task
   └── Perform Maintenance
   └── Update Maintenance Table

[System Lane]
   └── Generate Alerts
   └── Store Maintenance History
   └── Produce BI Reports

Diagram Suggestion

Swimlanes (Horizontal or Vertical)
----------------------------------
| Administrator | Supervisor | Technician | System |
-----------------------------------------------------
| Register Equipment           |             |       | 
| Assign Department            |             |       | 
|                              | Create Task |       | 
|                              | Assign Tech |       | 
|                              |             | Perform Maintenance |
|                              |             | Update Maintenance Table |
|                              |             |       | Generate Alerts & Reports |

. Each vertical column = actor

. Each rectangle = task/activity

. Arrows connect steps sequentially

